This MIT licence covers the application source code (src/, pipeline/) and
build configuration.

It does NOT cover:

- Generated chapter data (public/data/): derived from OpenGNT
  (https://github.com/eliranwong/OpenGNT) and therefore licensed under
  CC BY-SA 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/).
- Verse notes (content/notes/): original prose, licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0
  to remain compatible with the data they annotate and to keep community
  contributions shareable on equal terms.
- Fonts (public/fonts/): Cardo, licensed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1.
- Comparison translations (BSB, WEB, ASV, KJV) and the Dodson lexicon:
  public domain.
